s probed in this work induce competing galactic alignment signals for\nweak lensing, with opposite redshift and luminosity evolution. Understanding\nthe details of these intrinsic alignments will be key to exploit future major\ncosmic shear surveys like Euclid or LSST.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 17 Sep 2018 14:05:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-09-26"}
